  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick pan over medium heat.",
    "Butter one side of each slice of double-rise-bread.",
    "Place two slices of bread, butter side down, in the pan.",
    "Spread a layer of orange marmalade on each slice of bread in the pan.",
    "Top each slice with a sprinkle of chopped pistachio, diced scotch bonnet pepper, grated ginger, cinnamon, nutmeg, and salt.",
    "Place the remaining slices of bread, butter side up, on top of the filling.",
    "Cook for 2-3 minutes or until the bread is golden brown and the filling is warm.",
    "Flip the sandwiches over and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes or until the other side is also golden brown.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy."
  ],
